        {
            "_id": "XBz2toYQ5LlpBAkp",
            "img": "systems/pf2e/icons/actions/TwoActions.webp",
            "name": "Transpose",
            "sort": 1000000,
            "system": {
                "actionType": {
                    "value": "action"
                },
                "actions": {
                    "value": 2
                },
                "category": "offensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>The amalgamite teleports up to two destabilized creatures within 50 feet that they can see. They can either move a single creature to an unoccupied space or swap the positions of two creatures of the same size. If the amalgamite swaps two creatures, they can choose their self as one target. An unwilling creature can attempt a @Check[will|dc:33] save. If either target succeeds at this saving throw, both are unaffected.</p>"
                },
